Facebook profile picture update by Noorie Noor Ananta. Image created 24 October 2016 (16 days before demonetization). Contains: text 'SILENT MESSAGE' at top, large number '8' on right side, 'Nov Dec Jan' on left (the 3 months of demonetization chaos), two scorpion images at top corners, 'NOORIE RAI' at bottom left, date '24/10/16' at bottom right. Woman standing on a path. DECODED: 'SILENT MESSAGE' + 8 + Scorpions (8th zodiac) + 'Nov Dec Jan' (months affected) = complete prediction of November 8 demonetization and its 3-month aftermath. Scorpio is also PM Modi's zodiac sign. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Coded Signals — layered prediction of timing, zodiac connection, and duration.